      "role": "user",
      "content": "introspection or whatever... it doesnt feel like that. it feels like the light just went out. marc was the light. without him, i'm just going through the motions, eating, sleeping, working... but there's nothing behind it. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever will. it's just exhausting to keep pretending.",
